    "text": [
        "Dear Ruth,",
        "How're you darling? I hope everything is well with you. By the way,I intend putting up my TV set for sale and I thought I should inform you if you will want to buy.",
        "My husband just got promoted in his company to the position of a Director and has been transferred to their headquarter in Dubai. As a result, my family will be relocating in two weeks time so, we are selling off most of our belongings.I remembered you planned buying a secondhand TV set for your living room next week. I don't know if you would like ours.",
